    • 构造器详细资料

      • Name

        public Name(java.lang.String firstName,
            java.lang.String lastName)
        Construct a name from the given first and last names.
        参数:
        firstName - the first name (part) of the name
        lastName - the last name (part) of the name
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if either firstName or lastName is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if either firstName or lastName is empty

      • toString

        public java.lang.String toString()
        Returns a string representation of a name. The string representation is a first name and last name separated by a space character.
        覆盖:
        toString 在类中 java.lang.Object
        另请参阅:
        Object.toString(), for the string representation of a name

      • valueOf

        public static Name valueOf(java.lang.String name)
        Constructs an instance of Name from its string representation. The string representation of a Name is a first name and last name separated by a space character. It is assumed that first and last names do not themselves contain spaces.
        参数:
        name - a name in the specified string representation
        返回:
        an instance of a Name corresponding to the given string
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if name is null
        java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException - if there are not two component parts to name (first and last names)
